002package com.commercetools.api.client;
003
004import java.util.List;
005
006import io.vrap.rmf.base.client.RequestCommand;
007
008public interface ApiDeleteMethod<T extends ApiDeleteMethod<T, TResult>, TResult> extends RequestCommand<TResult> {
009    List<String> getVersion();
010
011    /**
012     * set version with the specificied value
013     * @param version resource version
014     * @param <TValue> value type
015     * @return method
016     */
017    <TValue> ApiDeleteMethod<T, TResult> withVersion(final TValue version);
018
019    /**
020     * add additional version query parameter
021     * @param version resource version
022     * @param <TValue> value type
023     * @return method
024     */
025    <TValue> ApiDeleteMethod<T, TResult> addVersion(final TValue version);
026
027    @SuppressWarnings("unchecked")
028    default T asBaseType() {
029        return (T) this;
030    }
031
032}
